SIMPLE: roofing
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Roofing
<hw>Roof"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of covering
with a roof.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The materials of which a roof is composed; materials
for a roof.</def> <rj><au>Gwilt.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Hence, the roof itself; figuratively, shelter.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Fit <xex>roofing</xex> gave.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Southey.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>The wedging, as of a horse or
car, against the top of an underground passage.</def>
<rj><au>Raymond.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Roofless</ent>⟦br⟧
